ive with four semesters worth of ASL instruction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/books...\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see:    / billvicars  \nTo learn basic fingerspelling see    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":54,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBIQ040EGAUiEwj4ypOnuOuTAxVoR_IAHT-RDN1I4Z2jofXH1IU7ygEE-a3c9Q==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqblFkMXhqelZwRDhRUUFwbzRzLWZYYTBCV1Vad3xBQ3Jtc0tsLTRpSWM1Q253WW1nWVFtZFlMRUNPV0dxcjZUMW5POThTejViWjNPbFZXWHR0SkFKUzJJcTlWSklJcmdORV9kaFBLdWtTX09ld3pHOHZXNWkwZTBIMGRvMEZHU0lqSnBFekx6a2R6ME84bW94VVBFbw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=OwtSP1QozuE","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqblFkMXhqelZwRDhRUUFwbzRzLWZYYTBCV1Vad3xBQ3Jtc0tsLTRpSWM1Q253WW1nWVFtZFlMRUNPV0dxcjZUMW5POThTejViWjNPbFZXWHR0SkFKUzJJcTlWSklJcmdORV9kaFBLdWtTX09ld3pHOHZXNWkwZTBIMGRvMEZHU0lqSnBFekx6a2R6ME84bW94VVBFbw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=OwtSP1QozuE","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":166,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBIQ040EGAUiEwj4ypOnuOuTAxVoR_IAHT-RDN1I4Z2jofXH1IU7ygEE-a3c9Q==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbHp3TDlhbDBCdGozMUdaaWpVdTRqRUx0WG5ud3xBQ3Jtc0trQm5sa0lmM3RtcDR1ajN2M3VXRzNuc2s0VWFSUURPeDRaalRqRlVYdVhURkpGa2padHdMWVg5dW5NSWgzLVJnSF9CMV85emhkRkx4TS1WMUtYODE2LWVIY1l0SXBEZG1fRUR1ek9aZjl3d1JBWGIxcw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.payp